           European Regional Expertise
         </h2>
         <p class="text-xl text-advisory-grey max-w-3xl mx-auto">
           Sophisticated understanding of regulatory landscapes across key European markets
         </p>
       </div>

       <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
         <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-slate-200 p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
           <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-european-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
             <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-european-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
               <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
             </svg>
           </div>
           <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Mittelstand AI Excellence</h3>
           <p class="text-advisory-grey mb-4">
             Systematic methodology respecting engineering precision whilst ensuring regulatory sophistication 
             for family-owned and PE-backed companies across German-speaking Europe
           </p>
           <div class="text-sm text-slate-500">
             Germany • Austria • Switzerland
           </div>
         </div>

         <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-slate-200 p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
           <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-compliance-green/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
             <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-compliance-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
               <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
             </svg>
           </div>
           <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Sustainable Innovation Leadership</h3>
