           </p>
         </div>

         <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-slate-200">
           <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Relationship Preservation</h3>
           <p class="text-sm text-advisory-grey">
             Enhancement rather than displacement of existing professional relationships
           </p>
         </div>

         <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-slate-200">
           <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Knowledge Transfer</h3>
           <p class="text-sm text-advisory-grey">
             Capability building ensuring internal team development alongside external expertise
           </p>
